      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "\ud83d\udcdd User Story: Configure Vendor Admin Table Columns with Drop-downs and Free-form Inputs"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "As A: Vendor Admin user"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "I Want To: Have each column in the Vendor Admin Table configured as either a drop-down or free-form input, according to specific requirements for each column"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "So That: Data entry is consistent, accurate, and matches customer requests for each field."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Acceptance Criteria (ACs)"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "AC1: Each column in the Vendor Admin Table must be configured as follows:"
            }
          ]
        },
