        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "AC2: Drop-down columns must only allow selection from the specified options."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "AC3: Free-form columns must allow any text input, with guidance on expected values where specified."
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "AC4: All changes must be reflected in the Vendor Admin Table UI and persist to the backend."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "AC5: Should default to blank status. User should be able to revert back to blank if they change their mind. Similar to how we set up drop downs in the Incident Admin. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Scenario Example"
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Input: User edits the \"W-9 Received\" cell for a vendor and selects \"YES\" from the drop-down."
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Output: The cell displays \"YES\" and the value is saved for that vendor."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Input: User enters \"2026-03-01\" in the \"Date Sent\" cell."
            },
            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Output: The cell displays \"2026-03-01\" and the value is saved for that vendor."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Original Description:"
