            {
              "type": "hardBreak"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "In Vendor Admin Table, I want these columns set up per the specific request per column. Most need to be a drop down within the cell. A few of them customer requested that they be free form. Please look at each column name and make the cells match their request."
            }
